This show is absolute brilliance with excellent plots adapted from the books and over the top performance by Benedict Cumberbatch and Martin Freeman.With 3 great seasons{Season 2 being the best} It is a masterpiece!!It is a must watch for those who are looking for fast paced thrilling actions and some amazing twists in the end that will blow your mind!!!!

PROS 

+Amazing Cast 

+Great Writing 

+Cumberbatch's portrayal of Sherlock 

+Martin Freeman's John Watson

+Jim Moriarty{One of the best antagonist I have ever seen} 

+Amazing Twists in the end!

CONS 

-Season 3's Antagonist was not so compelling 

-Abominable bride was the worst episode in this series 

Overall-9.8/10